== About me
I am a PhD student in robotics at [https://www.berkeley.edu/ University of California, Berkeley] adviced by [https://me.berkeley.edu/people/masayoshi-tomizuka/ Prof. Masayoshi Tomizuka].
I received B.S. in Mechanical Engineering from [https://umich.edu/ University of Michigan, Ann Arbor], 
and B.S. in Electrical and Computer Engineering from [http://ji.sjtu.edu.cn/ Joint Institute, Shanghai Jiao Tong University].

My research interest lies in *Robotics* (skill learning, control and optimization) and *Autonomous driving* (prediction, behavior generation).

